{
  "stem": "5470.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But because the fact that I was already there, I had to-- to bring the office into being, order all the stuff what we needed for the office and so on.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I was the only one, up until the 12th of October.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's where the office actually opened, and that's where he came and-- Who is he?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's Moss.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Moss was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was nasty, really nasty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was nasty with the Jewish people too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was trying to get as many people into the office as possible to keep them back from transport.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was Dutch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was [INAUDIBLE] from the beginning on with him, and the head of us came to know that and then [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was my luck actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He thought he could do better than the German contact person, and he thought that he could talk it over with him, and tell him what he wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's what the German contact person didn't like either.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he advised The Hague to get rid of him and said, yeah, who can then be appointed, because I was still of the same age?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was no other possibility.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then someone from The Hague came over, and he said, there is only one who can take over here and that was me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got the transfer to the leadership not straightaway but in actual fact, yes, but the appointment didn't follow up until the 1st of March, 1943.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, what want you to know from the organization of the camp?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We'll break for the end of the tape there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
